Definition LESS_OR_EQ autoloaded from theory `arithmetic`.
LESS_OR_EQ = |- !m n. m <= n = m < n \/ (m = n)

Theorem NOT_LESS autoloaded from theory `arithmetic`.
NOT_LESS = |- !m n. ~m < n = n <= m

